data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bed, 2 bath home with a 2-stall detached garage. Enjoy all the main floor has to offer with 3 bedrooms, updated full bath, cozy living & dining area plus kitchen with updated SS appliances! Downstairs you'll find a spacious basement that offers the perfect family room for relaxation and entertaining. The 4th bedroom, bathroom & large laundry/utility room completes the updated space. Location is everything- close proximity to schools, shops & the hospital!
